channel.title: Moparscape client error, need help. (Im using mac os 10.5.7)
channel.description:
Hello, my first post. :)
Anyways, Whenever I try to run the mopar client, it just quits. It tries to download the cache then it just quits after a minute. Also, when I go to moparisthebest.com, the java thingy comes up, and before the client shows, it just quits the web browser. Can someone help me? I am using a mac.
By the way, I just got this the split second I finished typing the above paragraph. This is what comes up after the downloading cache message:
[05:15:51] Error downloading news [05:15:52] Server : 127.0.0.1 [05:15:52] [05:15:52] [05:15:52] Loaded 0 random handlers [05:15:52] # Loading controllers
